{"tid":575823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊齊報考2019 DSE 為香港創造就業機會","createTime":"2018-02-28T12:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T07:12:33.000Z","uid":68080,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"507cf8faebfa5e43b8bf89f928bc22969729fa8f","tid":575823,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"既然政府幫大家埋單<br />\n點解唔報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先俾大家重温自己學生時代<br />\n最重要就 考評局收既錢有好大一部分會用黎請閱卷員、試場助理等等<br />\n<br />\n你一報 唔止免費考既人開心<br />\n考評局請班人又開心<br />\n你得閒既 直頭两家茶飯你都可以食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港要赢 2019DSE就要報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9602b5ba34db8b5536c4ef9809e55a51048d8eb","tid":575823,"uid":71883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">两</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">赢</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a45d747baf17ad9260fad65fabc2cfd9ecba033","tid":575823,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"報考人數急升 將會迫使考評局大量增加閱卷員、報到室主管、監考員、口試主考員等臨時人手<br />\n<br />\n對大學生黎講，最穩陣就係口試報到室主管，時薪132元，仲有gratuity。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然閱卷員、監考員、口試主考員亦可以考慮，但要求更高，當然相對應地人工會更高。<br />\n<br />\n而且需求上升得太多，人工有機會加得更高。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n報啦，全部人都報啦，又唔係你賣單<br />\n你創造緊就業機會俾香港啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCreates Jobs in HK<br />\nMake HK great again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cbb8834f75260932ca580a42a29dc0d7950285","tid":575823,"uid":7837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"波叔在下一盤很大的棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2594443a3035cc2bb9c7121185b2af8db7b24f71","tid":575823,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味 劏房波<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n對香港經濟有益既就一樣都唔肯做<br />\n你條仆街<br />\n而家連唯一全香港人都可以受惠既政策都cut埋<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbe50341628edc78242da0508032d6f2b0621c2","tid":575823,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2594443a3035cc2bb9c7121185b2af8db7b24f71","tid":575823,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味 劏房波<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n對香港經濟有益既就一樣都唔肯做<br />\n你條仆街<br />\n而家連唯一全香港人都可以受惠既政策都cut埋<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"5a234ba9d6bc2924a360b393cbea59fe1c9eeffe","tid":575823,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcbe50341628edc78242da0508032d6f2b0621c2","tid":575823,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo